org.dspace.eperson.dao

Interface GroupDAO

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DSpaceObjectDAO<Group>, DSpaceObjectLegacySupportDAO<Group>, GenericDAO<Group>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GroupDAOImpl

    public interface GroupDAO
extends DSpaceObjectDAO<Group>, DSpaceObjectLegacySupportDAO<Group>
    Database Access Object interface class for the Group object. The implementation of this class is responsible for all database calls for the Group object and is autowired by spring This class should only be accessed from a single service & should never be exposed outside of the API
    Author:
    kevinvandevelde at atmire.com
